summary: Arlette, a girl\'s name pronounced ar-LET. Ancient name of uncertain origin.
descriptionHtml:
Arlette, a girl\'s name pronounced ar-let. Ancient name of uncertain origin.
A Wood Elf with natural colors and a warpaint for forest camouflage.
A level 3 save game just finished the Golden claw quest, heading to Whiterun to see the Jarl early in the game.
 
If you like the look of her please download and enjoy. Thanks.

Mods used for this save game. Face, body and some items may differ or be missing if you do not use the mods listed below. ( Bonus Kantana sword, Wonderous Armor & Bows in the save ) All the mods listed below can be found here on Nexus. A big thank you to each everyone of their creators.

Extended_Slider_Colors - (not needed unless you wish to change her hair & skin color from my settings.)
Better_Females_by_Bella
Then add bella Less_Make_up_Version
Calientes_Female_Body_Mod_BBE
AOF_Believable_Hair
Natural_Eyes
BlackLight Katana standalone
Triss Armor Retextured
Shrouded Cowl-Hood Swap
